### About me.
I am currently research scholar at Robotic Institute in Carnegie Mellon University (CMU). I am also PhD student at Queensland University of Technology (QUT). My research interest is Computer Vision and Machine Learning. Please contact me via Email(abbasnejad.iman@gmail.com)
